==English==

===Adjective===
'''succinct'''
#[[brief]] and to the point; having characteristics of both brevity and clarity
#compressed into a tiny area
#''(archaic)''
##wrapped by, or as if by a girdle
##closely fitting, wound or wrapped or drawn up tightly

